AND THAT'S WHY WE DESTROYED SO

00:19:57.000 --> 00:20:02.000
MUCH ALREADY.

00:20:02.000 --> 00:20:04.000
WHEN THE... THE AGRICULTURE

00:20:04.000 --> 00:20:06.000
REVOLUTION BEGAN, AS YOU KNOW,

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:09.000
ABOUT 10,000 YEARS AGO, WE WENT

00:20:09.000 --> 00:20:11.000
FROM A HUNTER/GATHERER EXISTENCE

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:14.000
WHERE WE WERE MORE OR LESS IN

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:15.000
BALANCE-- WE WEREN'T WIPING OUT

00:20:15.000 --> 00:20:17.000
SPECIES AT ANY GREAT RATE-- TO

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:20.000
ONE IN WHICH WE BEGAN TO TURN

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:22.000
THE NATURAL ENVIRONMENTS,

00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:23.000
PARTICULARLY FORESTS AND THE

00:20:23.000 --> 00:20:24.000
GRASSLANDS, INTO AGRICULTURAL

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:27.000
FIELDS.

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:29.000
THAT PROCEEDED TO AN EXTENT THAT

00:20:29.000 --> 00:20:32.000
IT DID, DID FORM THE ECONOMIC

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:33.000
BASIS FOR GREAT HUMAN POPULATION

00:20:33.000 --> 00:20:35.000
GROWTH AND FOR THE EVOLUTION OF

00:20:35.000 --> 00:20:37.000
CIVILIZATION.

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:38.000
AND WHO CAN SAY THAT THAT'S NOT

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:40.000
A GOOD?

00:20:40.000 --> 00:20:42.000
IT'S JUST THAT HAVING... THAT IT

00:20:42.000 --> 00:20:43.000
TOOK A MILLION YEARS FOR

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:46.000
HUMANITY, YOU KNOW, COMING

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:48.000
THROUGH THESE EARLY STAGES

00:20:48.000 --> 00:20:51.000
STRUGGLING TO SURVIVE IN NATURE

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:52.000
TO FINALLY LEARN HOW TO BREAK

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:54.000
NATURE.

00:20:54.000 --> 00:20:56.000
AND WE DID THAT 10,000 YEARS

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:57.000
AGO, AND WE'RE CONTINUING TO

00:20:57.000 --> 00:21:00.000
BREAK IT.

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:01.000
AND NOW WE REALIZE THAT WE'VE

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:04.000
GOT TO PUT ON THE BRAKES AND

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:06.000
BRING THIS TO A HALT.

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:08.000
OTHERWISE WE'RE GOING TO BE

00:21:08.000 --> 00:21:10.000
DOWN.

