IT'S DOWN NOW... MANY OF THE

00:21:11.000 --> 00:21:15.000
NATURAL ECOSYSTEMS IN THE WORLD,

00:21:15.000 --> 00:21:16.000
THE MOST BEAUTIFUL ONES TOOK 10%

00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:17.000
OF WHAT IT WAS, AND WE'RE NOT

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:18.000
STOPPING.

00:21:18.000 --> 00:21:19.000
WE'RE GOING TO BE THROUGH THE

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:20.000
WHOLE BIT OF IT IN MANY PARTS OF

00:21:20.000 --> 00:21:21.000
THE WORLD UNLESS WE DO

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:22.000
SOMETHING.

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:23.000
IT'S JUST THAT WE'RE NEAR THE

00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:25.000
END OF NATURE IN MANY PARTS OF

00:21:25.000 --> 00:21:26.000
THE WORLD.

00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:27.000
Moyers: THE END OF NATURE.

