THE END OF... WHAT DO YOU MEAN

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:29.000
BY--

00:21:29.000 --> 00:21:30.000
I MEAN THE END OF A LARGE

00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:31.000
PART OF THE REST OF LIFE ON THE

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:33.000
PLANET.

