I MEAN, LET'S... NATURE WAS

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:43.000
DOING A PRETTY GOOD JOB BEFORE

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:44.000
WE ARRIVED AS THE LATECOMERS,

00:21:44.000 --> 00:21:46.000
RIGHT?

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:46.000
WONDERFULLY WELL.

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:49.000
Moyers: WONDERFULLY WELL.

00:21:49.000 --> 00:21:50.000
SO WHERE DID THIS IDEA COME FROM

00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:51.000
THAT WE'RE THE CROWN JEWEL OF

00:21:51.000 --> 00:21:54.000
CREATION?

00:21:54.000 --> 00:21:55.000
WELL, YOU KNOW, I SORT OF

00:21:55.000 --> 00:22:00.000
THINK WE ARE, IN ONE SENSE.

00:22:00.000 --> 00:22:01.000
THAT IS TO SAY, WE ARE THE BRAIN

00:22:01.000 --> 00:22:06.000
OF THE BIOSPHERE.

00:22:06.000 --> 00:22:09.000
WE ARE THE ONES THAT FINALLY,

00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:10.000
AFTER 4.5 BILLION YEARS OF

00:22:10.000 --> 00:22:12.000
EVOLUTION-- THAT'S WHAT IT TOOK

00:22:12.000 --> 00:22:15.000
TO GET WHERE WE ARE-- ACTUALLY

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:17.000
DEVELOPED ENOUGH POWER,

00:22:17.000 --> 00:22:20.000
REASONING POWER TO SEE WHAT'S

00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:23.000
HAPPENING TO UNDERSTAND THE

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:27.000
HISTORY THAT CREATED US AND TO

00:22:27.000 --> 00:22:27.000
REALIZE ALMOST TOO LATE WHAT

00:22:27.000 --> 00:22:33.000
WE'RE DOING.

00:22:33.000 --> 00:22:35.000
SO IN THE SENSE THAT WE ARE

00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:37.000
SOMETHING NEW UNDER THE SUN AND

00:22:37.000 --> 00:22:38.000
ON THE EARTH, WE HAVE AN

00:22:38.000 --> 00:22:40.000
ENORMOUS... WE'RE THE ONES THAT

00:22:40.000 --> 00:22:41.000
CAN DESTROY THE WORLD.

00:22:41.000 --> 00:22:41.000
NO OTHER SINGLE SPECIES EVER HAD

00:22:41.000 --> 00:22:44.000
ANYTHING LIKE THAT POWER.

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:45.000
WE HAVE THE POWER TO DESTROY THE

00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:48.000
WORLD, THE LIVING WORLD.

00:22:48.000 --> 00:22:49.000
AND WE ALSO HAVE THE KNOWLEDGE

00:22:49.000 --> 00:22:52.000
TO AVOID DOING IT.

00:22:52.000 --> 00:22:54.000
AND IT'S... IT'S SORT OF A RACE

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:57.000
TO THE FINISH LINE THAT WE WILL

00:22:57.000 --> 00:22:59.000
DEVELOP THE INTELLIGENCE AND THE

00:22:59.000 --> 00:23:03.000
POLICIES AND THE DECENCY TO

00:23:03.000 --> 00:23:06.000
BRING IT TO A HALT, NOT JUST FOR

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:08.000
LIFE ITSELF, BUT FOR FUTURE

00:23:08.000 --> 00:23:10.000
GENERATIONS BEFORE, YOU KNOW,

00:23:10.000 --> 00:23:12.000
THE JUGGERNAUT TAKES US OVER.

00:23:12.000 --> 00:23:14.000
Moyers: WHY ARE WE ESCALATING

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:16.000
SO RAPIDLY NOW THE DESTRUCTIVE

00:23:16.000 --> 00:23:16.000
IMPACT OF OUR BEHAVIOR?

00:23:16.000 --> 00:23:18.000
WHAT'S GOING ON?

00:23:18.000 --> 00:23:21.000
IT'S... IT'S MAINLY THAT

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:23.000
IT... WE'RE JUST BEING THE KIND

00:23:23.000 --> 00:23:25.000
OF RECKLESS, IGNORANT, UNCARING

00:23:25.000 --> 00:23:26.000
SPECIES WE'VE BEEN UP 'TIL NOW

00:23:26.000 --> 00:23:28.000
THAT'S DOING THE DAMAGE.

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:29.000
WE'RE STILL INCREASING IN

00:23:29.000 --> 00:23:31.000
NUMBERS.

00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:34.000
WE'RE AT 6.5 BILLION.

00:23:34.000 --> 00:23:36.000
HOWEVER, WE'RE GOING TO... WE'RE

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:37.000
SLOWING.

