Moyers: YEAH, THE PREDICTION

00:23:38.000 --> 00:23:39.000
IS THAT WHEN WE REACH NINE

00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:40.000
BILLION WE'LL BEGIN TO--

00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:43.000
YEAH, WE'LL PEAK.

