SO THAT'S 40% MORE THAN WHAT WE

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:46.000
HAVE NOW.

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:48.000
I THINK WE CAN HANDLE THAT.

00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:49.000
THAT RIGHT NOW IS A SERIOUS

00:23:49.000 --> 00:23:50.000
PROBLEM.

