BUT LET'S FIGURE OUT-- AND WE'VE

00:24:10.000 --> 00:24:12.000
GOT THE BRAINS TO DO IT-- OF HOW

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:14.000
TO INCREASE THE ECONOMY GROWING

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:15.000
AND THE QUALITY OF LIFE

