FOSSIL BASED OR NON-RENEWAL...

00:24:25.000 --> 00:24:25.000
RENEWABLE SOURCES OF ENERGY.

00:24:25.000 --> 00:24:27.000
IT'S AS SIMPLE AS THAT.

