00:27:13.000 --> 00:27:15.000
I THINK MOST PEOPLE MIGHT BE

00:27:15.000 --> 00:27:17.000
LISTENING TO US KNOW THE ANSWER.

00:27:17.000 --> 00:27:19.000
WE NEED LEADERSHIP.

00:27:19.000 --> 00:27:24.000
WE DESPERATELY NEED LEADERSHIP

00:27:24.000 --> 00:27:26.000
THAT WORKS OFF OF WHAT WE HAVE

00:27:26.000 --> 00:27:29.000
LEARNED THROUGH SCIENCE, THAT

00:27:29.000 --> 00:27:30.000
HAS PRODUCED A CONSENSUS ABOUT

00:27:30.000 --> 00:27:32.000
WHAT IS HAPPENING TO THE EARTH'S

00:27:32.000 --> 00:27:33.000
ENVIRONMENT, INCLUDING THE

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:36.000
LIVING CREATION.

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:37.000
AND SEES THE POTENTIAL IN IT AND

00:27:37.000 --> 00:27:40.000
NOT JUST THE NEED IN IT AND

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:43.000
GIVES, IN THIS COUNTRY

00:27:43.000 --> 00:27:46.000
ESPECIALLY, THE KIND OF VISION

00:27:46.000 --> 00:27:48.000
OF A FUTURE THAT WE CAN WORK FOR

00:27:48.000 --> 00:27:49.000
AS A PEOPLE TOWARD, AS A PEOPLE,

00:27:49.000 --> 00:27:50.000
THAT I THINK PEOPLE ARE HUNGRY

00:27:50.000 --> 00:27:52.000
FOR.

00:27:52.000 --> 00:27:53.000
Moyers: THERE IS A BIAS,

00:27:53.000 --> 00:27:54.000
THOUGH, AT THE MOMENT AGAINST

00:27:54.000 --> 00:27:56.000
SCIENCE THAT DISRUPTS OUR

00:27:56.000 --> 00:27:59.000
RELIGIOUS BELIEF OR SCIENCE THAT

00:27:59.000 --> 00:28:00.000
DIMINISHES OUR ECONOMIC GROWTH.

00:28:00.000 --> 00:28:02.000
RIGHT.

00:28:02.000 --> 00:28:05.000
BOTH BASED UPON MISCONCEPTIONS.

00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:07.000
Moyers: HOW SO?

00:28:07.000 --> 00:28:09.000
A GREENING OF AMERICA MEANS

00:28:09.000 --> 00:28:11.000
NEW MARKETS, NEW WAYS OF

00:28:11.000 --> 00:28:14.000
DEVELOPING RESOURCES, NEW

00:28:14.000 --> 00:28:17.000
TECHNOLOGIES, NEW DIRECTIONS,

00:28:17.000 --> 00:28:19.000
NEW ERAS OF EDUCATION, TRAINING,

00:28:19.000 --> 00:28:21.000
AND ON.

00:28:21.000 --> 00:28:24.000
SO AS FAR AS ECONOMY IS

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:27.000
CONCERNED, THAT'S A NO-BRAINER.

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:31.000
AS FAR AS RELIGION IS CONCERNED

00:28:31.000 --> 00:28:32.000
I HAVE... I HAVE A VERY

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:34.000
DIFFERENT VIEW FROM WHAT MANY

00:28:34.000 --> 00:28:36.000
SCIENTISTS AND ENVIRONMENTALISTS

00:28:36.000 --> 00:28:38.000
HAVE OF THE RELIGIOUS COMMUNITY.

00:28:38.000 --> 00:28:41.000
AND THAT IS, HAVING GROWN UP AS

00:28:41.000 --> 00:28:43.000
A SOUTHERN BAPTIST--

00:28:43.000 --> 00:28:43.000
Moyers: YOU ANSWERED THE

00:28:43.000 --> 00:28:44.000
ALTAR CALL.

00:28:44.000 --> 00:28:45.000
YOU WENT UNDER THE WATER.

00:28:45.000 --> 00:28:47.000
I DID.

00:28:47.000 --> 00:28:48.000
AND I GREW UP IN ONE OF THE

00:28:48.000 --> 00:28:50.000
REDDEST OF THE RED STATES.

00:28:50.000 --> 00:28:52.000
AND I HAVE THE HIGHEST RESPECT

00:28:52.000 --> 00:28:53.000
FOR THEM, YOU KNOW, FOLKS WHO

00:28:53.000 --> 00:28:55.000
ARE CALLED THESE DAYS EVEN

00:28:55.000 --> 00:28:58.000
FUNDAMENTALISTS AND THE 42% OF

00:28:58.000 --> 00:29:00.000
AMERICANS IDENTIFIED AS

00:29:00.000 --> 00:29:02.000
EVANGELICAL.

00:29:02.000 --> 00:29:03.000
I LIKE THEM.

00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:04.000
I THINK THEY'RE HIGHLY

00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:06.000
INTELLIGENT AND A LARGE

00:29:06.000 --> 00:29:08.000
PERCENTAGE OF THEM HIGHLY

00:29:08.000 --> 00:29:09.000
EDUCATED AND SO ON.

00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:13.000
SO IT'S ALWAYS OCCURRED TO ME

00:29:13.000 --> 00:29:15.000
THAT THE SCHISM BETWEEN

00:29:15.000 --> 00:29:17.000
SCIENTISTS, AGREED MOST ARE

00:29:17.000 --> 00:29:20.000
LIBERAL AND NON-BELIEVERS, AND

00:29:20.000 --> 00:29:21.000
THE GREAT MAJORITY OF AMERICANS,

00:29:21.000 --> 00:29:22.000
75%, YOU KNOW, WHO COULD BE

00:29:22.000 --> 00:29:26.000
CALLED RELIGIOUS TO SOME EXTENT

00:29:26.000 --> 00:29:29.000
WAS... MIGHT BE AN ARTIFACT.

00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:30.000
Moyers: WHAT DO YOU THINK YOU

00:29:30.000 --> 00:29:31.000
HAVE IN COMMON WITH CONSERVATIVE

00:29:31.000 --> 00:29:34.000
CHRISTIAN?

00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:35.000
WELL, ACTUALLY, JUST ABOUT

00:29:35.000 --> 00:29:37.000
EVERYTHING EXCEPT CERTAIN

00:29:37.000 --> 00:29:39.000
BELIEFS OF WHERE IT ALL CAME

00:29:39.000 --> 00:29:41.000
FROM AND WHO'S LOOKING OVER US.

00:29:41.000 --> 00:29:44.000
WE ARE MUCH CLOSER TOGETHER.

00:29:44.000 --> 00:29:45.000
I COULD GO DOWN, YOU KNOW, AND

00:29:45.000 --> 00:29:50.000
PICK A PASTOR FROM SOME SMALL

00:29:50.000 --> 00:29:53.000
COUNTRY CHURCH ALONG THE BYWAY

00:29:53.000 --> 00:29:54.000
OF THE HIGH... OF ALABAMA AND

00:29:54.000 --> 00:29:56.000
I'LL BET WE'D-- AS I SUGGESTED

00:29:56.000 --> 00:29:57.000
IN THAT BOOK-- WE SAT DOWN AND

00:29:57.000 --> 00:29:59.000
TALKED ABOUT OUR DEEPEST BELIEFS

00:29:59.000 --> 00:30:01.000
TOGETHER, WE'D COME UP WITH MORE

00:30:01.000 --> 00:30:02.000
AGREEMENTS, AGREEMENTS ON MORE

00:30:02.000 --> 00:30:05.000
THINGS THAN DISAGREEMENTS.

00:30:05.000 --> 00:30:05.000
AND THEN ISN'T IT THE AMERICAN

00:30:05.000 --> 00:30:06.000
WAY?

00:30:06.000 --> 00:30:08.000
WE COULD SAY, "LET'S PUT THAT

00:30:08.000 --> 00:30:09.000
ASIDE FOR AWHILE AND WORK

00:30:09.000 --> 00:30:10.000
TOGETHER WHEN WE REALLY HAVE

00:30:10.000 --> 00:30:11.000
SOMETHING WE NEED TO WORK

00:30:11.000 --> 00:30:13.000
TOGETHER ON."

00:30:13.000 --> 00:30:17.000
Moyers: YEAH, BUT, ED,

00:30:17.000 --> 00:30:18.000
BUT MANY OF THE CHRISTIANS WHO

00:30:18.000 --> 00:30:19.000
READ THE BIBLE LITERALLY REJECT

00:30:19.000 --> 00:30:20.000
THE CONCLUSION OF YOU SCIENTISTS

00:30:20.000 --> 00:30:20.000
THAT WE'VE EVOLVED FROM LOWER

00:30:20.000 --> 00:30:22.000
FORMS.

00:30:22.000 --> 00:30:23.000
I MEAN, THEY BELIEVE THE EARTH

00:30:23.000 --> 00:30:24.000
IS NOT OUR HOME.

00:30:24.000 --> 00:30:26.000
WE'RE HEAVEN BOUND.

00:30:26.000 --> 00:30:27.000
SOME OF THEM BELIEVE THE SECOND

00:30:27.000 --> 00:30:29.000
COMING OF JESUS IS SO

00:30:29.000 --> 00:30:30.000
IMMINENT...

00:30:30.000 --> 00:30:30.000
I KNOW.

00:30:30.000 --> 00:30:32.000
Moyers: ...THAT CARING FOR

00:30:32.000 --> 00:30:34.000
THE EARTH IS OF LITTLE

00:30:34.000 --> 00:30:35.000
CONSEQUENCE.

00:30:35.000 --> 00:30:37.000
BUT YOU...

00:30:37.000 --> 00:30:38.000
NOW...

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:38.000
Moyers: ...YOU ADDRESSED THIS

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:39.000
BOOK, YOUR LATEST BOOK, "THE

00:30:39.000 --> 00:30:41.000
CREATION: AN APPEAL TO SAVE LIFE

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:42.000
ON EARTH," TO A SOUTHERN BAPTIST

00:30:42.000 --> 00:30:45.000
PASTOR.

00:30:45.000 --> 00:30:45.000
YOU AND I KNOW MANY OF THEM.

00:30:45.000 --> 00:30:46.000
YES.

00:30:46.000 --> 00:30:47.000
Moyers: WE GREW UP WITH THEM.

00:30:47.000 --> 00:30:48.000
YES.

00:30:48.000 --> 00:30:49.000
Moyers: WHY DID YOU WRITE

00:30:49.000 --> 00:30:50.000
THIS BOOK TO A SOUTHERN BAPTIST

00:30:50.000 --> 00:30:54.000
PASTOR?

00:30:54.000 --> 00:30:55.000
WELL, I DID PARTLY BECAUSE

00:30:55.000 --> 00:30:57.000
THAT'S MY BACKGROUND.

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:58.000
ALTHOUGH, I'M NOW A SECULAR

00:30:58.000 --> 00:31:00.000
HUMANIST.

00:31:00.000 --> 00:31:01.000
A REAL... A THOROUGH GOING

00:31:01.000 --> 00:31:02.000
SECULARIST.

00:31:02.000 --> 00:31:03.000
IT'S MY BACKGROUND.

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:05.000
I UNDERSTOOD IT.

00:31:05.000 --> 00:31:07.000
I RESPECTED GREATLY THE PEOPLE

00:31:07.000 --> 00:31:10.000
OF THE CULTURE I GREW UP IN.

00:31:10.000 --> 00:31:12.000
BUT ALSO, THERE WAS THE NEW YORK

00:31:12.000 --> 00:31:12.000
EFFECT, WHAT I CALL THE NEW YORK

00:31:12.000 --> 00:31:14.000
EFFECT.

00:31:14.000 --> 00:31:16.000
IN ADDRESSING EVANGELICALS

00:31:16.000 --> 00:31:18.000
INSTEAD OF UNITARIANS.

00:31:18.000 --> 00:31:19.000
( LAUGHTER )

00:31:19.000 --> 00:31:20.000
Moyers: WELL, THERE'S A LOT

00:31:20.000 --> 00:31:22.000
MORE OF 'EM FOR ONE THING.

00:31:22.000 --> 00:31:23.000
( LAUGHTER )

00:31:23.000 --> 00:31:23.000
THERE ARE MORE BAPTISTS IN TEXAS

00:31:23.000 --> 00:31:24.000
THAN THERE ARE PEOPLE, AND I

00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:25.000
GUESS THAT'S PROBABLY TRUE OF

00:31:25.000 --> 00:31:25.000
ALABAMA.

00:31:25.000 --> 00:31:29.000
SO, YOU ADDRESSED THEM...

00:31:29.000 --> 00:31:30.000
BECAUSE THEY'RE MUSCULAR.

00:31:30.000 --> 00:31:30.000
THEY'RE POWERFUL.

00:31:30.000 --> 00:31:31.000
WELL, ALSO  AS I SAY, THE NEW

00:31:31.000 --> 00:31:32.000
YORK EFFECT IS THAT IF YOU CAN

00:31:32.000 --> 00:31:33.000
MAKE IT IN NEW YORK, YOU CAN

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:33.000
MAKE IT ANYWHERE.

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:34.000
IN OTHER WORDS, IF YOU CAN MAKE

00:31:34.000 --> 00:31:35.000
IT WITH SOUTHERN BAPTISTS, YOU

00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:36.000
CAN MAKE IT ANYWHERE.

00:31:36.000 --> 00:31:38.000
AND THE ARGUMENT I MAKE IN THE

00:31:38.000 --> 00:31:41.000
CREATION IS EXTREMELY SIMPLE.

00:31:41.000 --> 00:31:43.000
IT'S THAT IT IS... I SAID "LET

00:31:43.000 --> 00:31:48.000
US IN THE SERVICE OF A

00:31:48.000 --> 00:31:53.000
TRANSCENDENT MORAL OBLIGATION

00:31:53.000 --> 00:31:56.000
AND CONCERN PUT ASIDE OUR

00:31:56.000 --> 00:31:58.000
DIFFERENCES FOR THE TIME BEING

00:31:58.000 --> 00:32:00.000
AND NOT FUSS WITH EACH OTHER

00:32:00.000 --> 00:32:02.000
OVER EVOLUTION, IN OTHER WORDS

00:32:02.000 --> 00:32:03.000
WHERE IT ALL CAME FROM.

00:32:03.000 --> 00:32:05.000
LET US AGREE LOOKING AT THE

00:32:05.000 --> 00:32:09.000
EVIDENCE THAT IS DISAPPEARING.

00:32:09.000 --> 00:32:11.000
AND LET US, DARE I USE THE WORD,

00:32:11.000 --> 00:32:13.000
GATHER AT THE RIVER."

00:32:13.000 --> 00:32:16.000
COME TOGETHER ON COMMON GROUND

00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:20.000
WHERE WE CAN EXERCISE THE

00:32:20.000 --> 00:32:21.000
EXTRAORDINARY POWER WE HAVE

00:32:21.000 --> 00:32:24.000
JOINTLY.

00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:26.000
AND I ARGUE AND FEW PEOPLE

00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:27.000
DISAGREED WITH ME THAT SCIENCE

00:32:27.000 --> 00:32:29.000
AND RELIGION ARE THE TWO MOST

00:32:29.000 --> 00:32:30.000
POWERFUL SOCIAL FORCES IN THE

00:32:30.000 --> 00:32:33.000
WORLD.

00:32:33.000 --> 00:32:35.000
HAVING THEM AT ODDS AT EACH

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:37.000
OTHER ALL THE WAY UP TO THE

00:32:37.000 --> 00:32:40.000
HIGHEST LEVELS OF GOVERNMENT AND

00:32:40.000 --> 00:32:41.000
THE POPULAR MEDIA ALL THE TIME

00:32:41.000 --> 00:32:45.000
IS NOT PRODUCTIVE.

00:32:45.000 --> 00:32:47.000
Moyers: IN YOUR BOOK, YOU ASK

00:32:47.000 --> 00:32:48.000
BOTH SCIENCE AND RELIGION TO SET

00:32:48.000 --> 00:32:49.000
ASIDE THEIR DIFFERENCES ABOUT

00:32:49.000 --> 00:32:53.000
METAPHYSICAL ISSUES.

00:32:53.000 --> 00:32:54.000
MEET ON THE NEAR SIDE OF

00:32:54.000 --> 00:32:55.000
METAPHYSICS.

00:32:55.000 --> 00:32:56.000
Moyers: MEET ON THE NEAR SIDE

00:32:56.000 --> 00:32:57.000
OF METAPHYSICS.

00:32:57.000 --> 00:32:57.000
RIGHT.

00:32:57.000 --> 00:32:58.000
Moyers: BUT CAN YOU ASK

00:32:58.000 --> 00:32:59.000
RELIGION TO DO THAT WHEN BY

00:32:59.000 --> 00:33:02.000
NATURE RELIGION IS CONCERNED

00:33:02.000 --> 00:33:04.000
WITH THE METAPHYSICAL, WITH

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:07.000
UNSEEN DEITIES?

00:33:07.000 --> 00:33:09.000
SURE, YOU CAN.

00:33:09.000 --> 00:33:11.000
YOU KNOW, I HAVE A LOT OF

00:33:11.000 --> 00:33:12.000
PHYSICISTS FRIENDS WORKING ON

00:33:12.000 --> 00:33:14.000
STRING THEORY WHO ARE ALSO

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:15.000
PREOCCUPIED WITH THINGS THEY

00:33:15.000 --> 00:33:17.000
CAN'T SEE OR MEASURE.

00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:18.000
BUT HOWEVER, THE POINT HERE IS

00:33:18.000 --> 00:33:25.000
YES YOU CAN AND WE'VE DONE IT.

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:26.000
TO IMAGINE A WORLD WHERE

00:33:26.000 --> 00:33:27.000
SCIENCE AND RELIGION CORPORATE

00:33:27.000 --> 00:33:28.000
TOGETHER.

00:33:28.000 --> 00:33:30.000
Moyers: IT WAS THAT LAST YEAR

00:33:30.000 --> 00:33:31.000
ED WILSON PLAYED AN IMPORTANT

00:33:31.000 --> 00:33:32.000
ROLE IN ORGANIZING A COALITION

00:33:32.000 --> 00:33:34.000
OF SCIENTISTS AND EVANGELICAL

00:33:34.000 --> 00:33:35.000
CHRISTIANS TO MEET ON GLOBAL

00:33:35.000 --> 00:33:36.000
WARMING AND HABITAT

00:33:36.000 --> 00:33:39.000
PRESERVATION.

00:33:39.000 --> 00:33:40.000
WE WILL NOT ALLOW EVANGELICAL

00:33:40.000 --> 00:33:43.000
CHRISTIANS WITH SCIENTIST TODAY,

00:33:43.000 --> 00:33:44.000
WE WILL NOT ALLOW IT THE,

00:33:44.000 --> 00:33:48.000
CREATION, TO BE DEGRADED,

00:33:48.000 --> 00:33:53.000
DESTROYED BY HUMAN FOLLY.

00:33:53.000 --> 00:33:56.000
Moyers: YOU SAY YOU'RE A

00:33:56.000 --> 00:34:00.000
SECULAR HUMANIST.

00:34:00.000 --> 00:34:01.000
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO HEAR WHEN

00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:03.000
YOU SAY THAT?

00:34:03.000 --> 00:34:04.000
WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT?

00:34:04.000 --> 00:34:05.000
THAT TERM DRIVES THE

00:34:05.000 --> 00:34:06.000
EVANGELICAL, THE CHRISTIAN RIGHT

00:34:06.000 --> 00:34:08.000
INTO A FRENZY.

00:34:08.000 --> 00:34:09.000
A HUMANIST IS A PERSON WHO

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:12.000
BELIEVES THAT IN MATTERS ETHICAL

00:34:12.000 --> 00:34:20.000
AND IN MATTERS OF ESTHETIC AND

00:34:20.000 --> 00:34:23.000
CENTRAL CONCERN SHOULD PUT

00:34:23.000 --> 00:34:26.000
HUMANITY AS THE FIRST AND FINAL

00:34:26.000 --> 00:34:30.000
PURPOSE OF IT ALL.

00:34:30.000 --> 00:34:31.000
THAT WE HAVE JUST THIS ONE

00:34:31.000 --> 00:34:34.000
PLANET TO LIVE.

00:34:34.000 --> 00:34:36.000
WE ARE NOT BEING LOOKED OVER.

00:34:36.000 --> 00:34:37.000
BUT WE ARE ON OUR OWN,

00:34:37.000 --> 00:34:38.000
ESSENTIALLY.

00:34:38.000 --> 00:34:39.000
AND WE ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR

00:34:39.000 --> 00:34:41.000
OURSELVES AND WE BETTER GET

00:34:41.000 --> 00:34:43.000
TOGETHER AS A SPECIES AND WORK

00:34:43.000 --> 00:34:44.000
IT OUT AND STOP RELYING ON

00:34:44.000 --> 00:34:46.000
SUPERNATURAL POWERS.

00:34:46.000 --> 00:34:47.000
THAT'S BASICALLY WHAT HUMANISM

00:34:47.000 --> 00:34:48.000
IS.

00:34:48.000 --> 00:34:50.000
Moyers: YOU DESCRIBE THE

00:34:50.000 --> 00:34:51.000
WORLD AS IT IS AND YET, YOU'RE

00:34:51.000 --> 00:34:52.000
NOT A MAN WHO'S A... YOU'RE NOT

00:34:52.000 --> 00:34:54.000
A PESSIMIST.

00:34:54.000 --> 00:34:55.000
YOU'RE... THERE'S A LOT OF HOPE

00:34:55.000 --> 00:35:01.000
IN THE CREATION.

00:35:01.000 --> 00:35:03.000
WHAT CAN WE DO TO TRY TO MAKE A

00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:08.000
DIFFERENCE ON THE FOOTPRINT THAT

00:35:08.000 --> 00:35:09.000
WE HUMANS ARE LEAVING ON THIS

00:35:09.000 --> 00:35:11.000
EARTH?

00:35:11.000 --> 00:35:12.000
I THINK PROBABLY IT GOES

00:35:12.000 --> 00:35:13.000
DOWN... LET'S GO DOWN ONE LAYER

00:35:13.000 --> 00:35:14.000
OF THOUGHT FROM WHAT WE HAD

00:35:14.000 --> 00:35:15.000
EARLIER, AND GO TO THE DEEPEST

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:16.000
LEVEL.

00:35:16.000 --> 00:35:18.000
IF WE COULD CHANGE OUR

00:35:18.000 --> 00:35:19.000
WORLDVIEW, IT WOULD BE SOMEWHAT

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:21.000
RADICAL.

00:35:21.000 --> 00:35:24.000
IT WOULD MEAN SEEING OURSELVES

00:35:24.000 --> 00:35:26.000
AS A BIOLOGICAL SPECIES IN A

00:35:26.000 --> 00:35:30.000
BIOLOGICAL WORLD.

00:35:30.000 --> 00:35:32.000
THAT WE ARE A SPECIES

00:35:32.000 --> 00:35:35.000
EXQUISITELY WELL ADAPTED TO THIS

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:39.000
PLANET AND THAT WE ORIGINATED

00:35:39.000 --> 00:35:42.000
HERE AND THAT OUR PECULIARITIES,

00:35:42.000 --> 00:35:43.000
INCLUDING THE ONES THAT THREATEN

00:35:43.000 --> 00:35:45.000
US ALL THE TIME, THAT THREATEN

00:35:45.000 --> 00:35:46.000
YOUR OWN... THREATEN OUR OWN

00:35:46.000 --> 00:35:48.000
EXISTENCE ARE... CAN BE

00:35:48.000 --> 00:35:49.000
UNDERSTOOD BY THE HISTORY OF THE

00:35:49.000 --> 00:35:50.000
WAY WE ORIGINATED IN THAT LIVING

00:35:50.000 --> 00:35:52.000
WORLD.

00:35:52.000 --> 00:35:53.000
AND IF WE COULD JUST PLACE

00:35:53.000 --> 00:35:55.000
OURSELVES REALISTICALLY IN THAT

00:35:55.000 --> 00:35:58.000
CONTEXT AND STOP THINKING OF

00:35:58.000 --> 00:35:59.000
OURSELVES AS SEMI ANGELS, YOU

00:35:59.000 --> 00:36:02.000
KNOW, ON THE WAY... THAT THIS IS

00:36:02.000 --> 00:36:03.000
JUST A WEIGH STATION ON A WAY ON

00:36:03.000 --> 00:36:07.000
UP TO AN IDEALIZED EXISTENCE,

00:36:07.000 --> 00:36:08.000
CHANGE THAT.

00:36:08.000 --> 00:36:10.000
THEN I THINK WE WOULD GET PRETTY

00:36:10.000 --> 00:36:14.000
SERIOUS ABOUT PEACE AND LONG

00:36:14.000 --> 00:36:15.000
TERM SECURITY AND SAVING THE

00:36:15.000 --> 00:36:18.000
REST OF LIFE.

00:36:18.000 --> 00:36:18.000
AND... AND KEEPING OUR OPTIONS

00:36:18.000 --> 00:36:21.000
OPEN FOR THE FUTURE.

00:36:21.000 --> 00:36:22.000
Moyers: E.O. WILSON, THANK

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:23.000
YOU VERY MUCH FOR JOINING ME ON

00:36:23.000 --> 00:36:24.000
THE JOURNAL.

