VIOLENCE HAS CLAIMED THE LIVES

00:54:11.000 --> 00:54:12.000
OF MORE MEMBERS OF THE EARTH

00:54:12.000 --> 00:54:14.000
CONSERVATION CORPS.

00:54:14.000 --> 00:54:16.000
ONE OF THEM WAS 19-YEAR-OLD

00:54:16.000 --> 00:54:17.000
AARON TEETER, A BUDDING

00:54:17.000 --> 00:54:18.000
FILMMAKER WHEN HE WAS GUNNED

00:54:18.000 --> 00:54:20.000
DOWN LAST APRIL.

00:54:20.000 --> 00:54:21.000
HE WAS A HIGH SCHOOL DROPOUT

00:54:21.000 --> 00:54:22.000
WITH TIME IN JUVENILE DETENTION

00:54:22.000 --> 00:54:24.000
FOR DEALING DRUGS.

00:54:24.000 --> 00:54:25.000
WHEN HE JOINED THE EARTH

00:54:25.000 --> 00:54:26.000
CONSERVATION CORPS, HIS LIFE

00:54:26.000 --> 00:54:28.000
BEGAN TO TURN AROUND.

00:54:28.000 --> 00:54:30.000
HE GOT INTERESTED IN JOURNALISM

00:54:30.000 --> 00:54:31.000
AND BEGAN PRODUCING STORIES

00:54:31.000 --> 00:54:33.000
ABOUT SCHOOL CONDITIONS,

00:54:33.000 --> 00:54:34.000
DETENTION CENTERS AND EFFORTS TO

00:54:34.000 --> 00:54:36.000
KEEP TEENS OUT OF JAIL.

00:54:36.000 --> 00:54:38.000
HE WAS WORKING ON A DOCUMENTARY

00:54:38.000 --> 00:54:39.000
ABOUT GUNS WHEN HE WAS SHOT

00:54:39.000 --> 00:54:41.000
DEAD.

00:54:41.000 --> 00:54:42.000
TWO SUSPECTS IN THE MURDER ARE

00:54:42.000 --> 00:54:45.000
NOW AWAITING TRIAL.

00:54:45.000 --> 00:54:46.000
JEROME SCOTT, THE BRIGHT KID WHO

00:54:46.000 --> 00:54:48.000
WANTED TO WORK WITH ANIMALS, WON

00:54:48.000 --> 00:54:49.000
A FULL SCHOLARSHIP TO THE

00:54:49.000 --> 00:54:51.000
UNIVERSITY OF ARKANSAS AT LITTLE

00:54:51.000 --> 00:54:52.000
ROCK-- AN HONOR HE DIDN'T LIVE

00:54:52.000 --> 00:54:54.000
TO ENJOY.

00:54:54.000 --> 00:54:56.000
HE DIED OF LEUKEMIA, UNDIAGNOSED

00:54:56.000 --> 00:54:59.000
UNTIL THE DAY IT KILLED HIM.

00:54:59.000 --> 00:55:00.000
THE UNIVERSITY ESTABLISHED A

00:55:00.000 --> 00:55:02.000
SCHOLARSHIP IN JEROME'S NAME.

00:55:02.000 --> 00:55:04.000
ITS FIRST RECIPIENT IS ANOTHER

00:55:04.000 --> 00:55:05.000
MEMBER OF THE EARTH CONSERVATION

00:55:05.000 --> 00:55:07.000
CORPS, DEREK OSHIN.

